reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute and entertaining for my 3 month old.
reviews.reviewText: This car seat/stroller plush activity is exactly as expected. I like that it wraps around the bar and stays in place on the car seat. It's just enough to entertain my 3 month old on car rides when he is fussy. He likes to pull at the toys. It is in no way made for teething but the baby can bite the plush part. The toys are mostly hard plastics. I'm happy with it.
